 @1sdani  Specifically this seems to be a parody of the old Woodsy Owl ads. 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gZB7gSQRIuM
Watch this one and you'll notice the parallels.  A group of kids following our hero across the town in an effort to stop pollution, with a sing-songy cutesy jingle. You may even notice both ads share a closeup on the mascot's hand picking up a piece of garbage and then a wide shot of them tossing it into a garbage can.

